    "colors" : {
      "comment" : "Category overlay – unit"
    },
    "Colors are not a currency. Well — kind of. You can earn up to 100 per day. Steps and sleep give them to you automatically. Body, mind, and heart — you add those yourself. You can spend colors to unlock apps. But the more you spend, the less colorful your canvas becomes. Because doomscrolling takes color out of life. Literally, here.\n\nI'm not selling them through microtransactions. Colors are yours. You earn them, you deserve them, you can always add more. Within limits." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_colors"
    },
