    "Error" : {
      "comment" : "ProfileEditor – error alert title"
    },
    "Every day is 24 hours. But no two are the same. The canvas is proof of that — a record of what actually happened, not what you planned. The more you lived, the more it shows. It reacts to your sleep and steps. The more you sleep, the darker it gets. The more you walk, the brighter. Your actions throughout the day shape it, and every 24 hours the canvas resets — unique, every single time." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_canvas"
    },
