    "Feedback" : {

    },
    "Feeds" : {
      "comment" : "Tab bar title"
    },
    "Feeds are not evil. They're just expensive. Every minute inside them drains color from the day. That's the deal — open your banned apps, watch the canvas fade. The choice is always yours. I just made it visible. You can unlock apps through the notification that pops up when you try to open a blocked one, through this app, or through the widget." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_feeds"
    },
