    "Sleep hours" : {

    },
    "Sleep is the frame around every day. Everything else fits inside it. Set your desired sleep time, and if you hit it — you earn 20 colors. Data comes from the Health app. Sometimes Apple is slow to sync. Not my fault." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_sleep"
