    "Steps" : {
      "comment" : "StepBalanceCard – steps chip label"
    },
    "Steps and sleep come from the Health app and are the same for everyone. Body, mind and heart are activities you add by tapping the + button at the bottom of the screen." : {

    },
    "Steps are not a fitness metric. They are proof that your body moved through the world today. The more you moved, the brighter everything gets. Set your own step goal and earn 20 colors when you reach it. You don't have to do 10k. It's your number." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_steps"
